Enum DimensionPlusUtility.ErrorMessage

  • java.lang.Object

    DimensionPlusUtility

    public static enum DimensionPlusUtility.ErrorMessage
extends java.lang.Enum<DimensionPlusUtility.ErrorMessage>
    ErrorMessage is error flag that will show the current process error status.

    The following errors are currently defined:

    NO_ERROR: No error has been met during this processing.

    NULL_PATH: The path string is null.

    INVALID_PARAMETER: Input parameter is invalid.

    INVALID_PATH: Input path is invalid.

    DUAL_LENS_NO_SUPPORTED: Dual lens engine doesn't support at this platform. This operation will be terminated.

    DUAL_LENS_BUSY: Dual lens engine is busy. This operation will be terminated.

    READFILE_ERROR: The input file is not DualLens or DimensionPlus format.
